      • RemoveAtribute

        @Deprecated
public void RemoveAtribute(javafx.scene.Node atribute,
                                        java.lang.String name)
        Deprecated. 
        THIS FUNCTION WILL BE REMOVED USE WindowBase#AddAtribute(Node) instead.
        Parameters:
        atribute - | Attribute what will be removed.
        name - | Name of its UpdateHandler. Use this only when you named update handler. For example: 
         Label label = new Label("attribute to removeeee");
 
 panel.AddAtributeWithCustomUpdate(new UpdateHandler(label, "updater123")
 {
                public void Handle(double windowX, double windowY, double width, double height)
                {
                        label.setTranslateX(windowX+40);
                        label.setTranslateY(windowY+15);
                }
 });
 
 panel.RemoveAtribute(label);
        Since:
        1.2.0
